vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to SL3 Trinity, LP for the use of a total of approximately 2,619 square feet of land to occupy, maintain and utilize two benches, two trash receptacles, six street lights, ten trees and landscape and irrigation on a portion of Singleton Boulevard right-of-way located near its intersection with Conklin Street and Crossman Avenue - Revenue: General Fund $500.00 one-time fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
